# AI Layer

- Route all AI calls through `UnifiedAIService` in `src/services/backendAIService.ts`.
- Model types and provider config: import from `shared/aiModels.ts` only.
- Cost calculation: import from `shared/costCalculator.ts` only.
- Do not add duplicate `useAIService` hooks or parallel AI service classes.
- User API keys → client `AIService`; shared/env keys → backend `/api/ai/generate`.
- Prompt templates live in `src/utils/promptGenerator.ts`; keep prompts out of components.
